item.title: André 3000
item.description: André Lauren Benjamin, better known by his stage name André 3000, is an American musician and actor best known for being a part of hip hop duo Outkast alongside fellow rapper Big Boi. As an actor, Benjamin has made appearances in a number of films and television series, including Families, The Shield, Be Cool, Revolver, Semi-Pro, Four Brothers, and in the lead role of Jimi Hendrix in All Is by My Side. He is widely considered among the greatest rappers of all time.
